1. Introduction
The BasicLine S3 – Industrial is an intelligent controller designed for industrial compressor cooling systems.
It controls up to six fans, a spray cooling system, and a reverse cycle for lamella cleaning, while monitoring efficiency and system health.
Firmware version v1.3.0 adds full diagnostics, web interface, data logging, and a watchdog for continuous operation.



