3. Safety Information
Important installation and operating notes:
Power supply 12–24 V DC with fuse protection.
Relay contacts rated for max. 250 V AC / 10 A.
Always disconnect power before servicing.
Install temperature sensors with thermal paste.
Do not connect mains voltage to signal inputs.
Web interface does not require Internet access.
Factory Reset restores default configuration.



